<script type="text/javascript">
/*
 * Javascript Diff Algorithm
 *  By John Resig (http://ejohn.org/)
 *  Modified by Chu Alan "sprite"
 *  Hacked to suit SiteScape by Joe DeStefano
 *
 * More Info:
 *  http://ejohn.org/projects/javascript-diff-algorithm/
